The postmaster has received a municipal contract for a full route survey of Sepulcher Pasture, where funeral paths and reclaimed farm tracks keep shifting under bellwind erosion. Map every passable section so Midgaard couriers can move legal notices without losing runners to dead-end lanes.
Your Sepulcher Pasture atlas has been stamped and archived in the civic records office. Courier supervisors have begun issuing your route sheet to night-shift runners assigned to pasture deliveries.
